United Country Moody Realty, Inc. Mountain Home

data.description: Dream home alert! This stunning 3 bedroom, 2 bath home offers a spacious 2292 sqft of pure comfort. On a generous 1.90 acres surrounded by pasture you’ll love the space and peacefulness this land has to offer plus its only minutes away from town! Step inside and be greeted by a pristine interior, fresh paint, new trim throughout and fresh flooring. The heart of this home is its open-concept layout, allowing for seamless interaction between living, dining and kitchen areas. Whether you’re hosting a cozy family gathering or entertaining friends, this well-designed space ensures everyone feels connected and at ease. You’ll be delighted to find all new appliances, central vac, and granite countertops that make meal preparation a breeze. But the wonders don’t end there! This property also features a fantastic 30X40 concrete floor shop that provides great storage for vehicles, workshop crafts, or hobbies. Don’t miss this opportunity to make this house your perfect home sweet home!
